{"tid":1190671,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"安倍晉三妻子熱愛大麻，WHO:CBD不是毒品","createTime":"2019-06-07T12:41:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T14:44:21.000Z","uid":32511,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ba2234ad3eda9910dc70194580a3e25b130d36d1","tid":1190671,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T12:41:37.000Z","msg":"在2015 年，安倍晉三的妻子安倍昭惠在表達了對大麻的熱愛，並表示如果法律允許的話，她很樂意自己落手種一些大麻。「雖然日本還沒有允許，但我認為大麻也可以用於醫療用途。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/lNhLDuNKURc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FlNhLDuNKURc&d=SmQqe2lJFulj5u2s5Cv8ummu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=171382f5\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/lNhLDuNKURc</a><br />\n<br />\n世界衛生組織(WHO)：含有不超過0.2％THC的CBD和純CBD製劑不會以任何方式列入國際藥物管制公約。<br />\n<br />\n日本當地仍將大麻視為毒品，但從大麻當中提煉的大麻二酚（Cannabidiol，CBD）產品目前能夠在當地合法銷售。CBD 是醫療用大麻當中最具醫療價值的一種成分，有保護神經、改善皮膚發炎、抗氧化、舒緩皮膚敏感泛紅、為皮膚表層建立保護屏障、改善皮膚自我修復力，治療濕疹等疾病，對老年人群應該特別有幫助。"},{"pid":"55bb0e3dac72b88a50973eac8ad0034a894af71f","tid":1190671,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T12:41:59.000Z","msg":"香港有冇禁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54f467873f8f5a1e3db1068788d32db9d1c1fd0e","tid":1190671,"uid":522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"55bb0e3dac72b88a50973eac8ad0034a894af71f","tid":1190671,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T12:41:59.000Z","msg":"香港有冇禁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T12:47:35.000Z","msg":"THC有，CBD無寫明"},{"pid":"4b116345d8301e5fbcd80bff530734952a053463","tid":1190671,"uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T15:22:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ox6hWUC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOx6hWUC.png&h=0ae5e8b7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"29ec2a20aa0eb479d37c2aa2f8301e2f1db51a2e","tid":1190671,"uid":3578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"54f467873f8f5a1e3db1068788d32db9d1c1fd0e","tid":1190671,"uid":522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"55bb0e3dac72b88a50973eac8ad0034a894af71f","tid":1190671,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T12:41:59.000Z","msg":"香港有冇禁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T12:47:35.000Z","msg":"THC有，CBD無寫明"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T14:34:02.000Z","msg":"CBD冇禁到"},{"pid":"133f43b80eb5403d288326059dca25ef3b66ef39","tid":1190671,"uid":251712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T14:44:21.000Z","msg":"lm"}]}